    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sleeveless apronlike garments which have a skirt and a bodice portion and which cover the front, sides, and a portion of the back. Worn over main garments for protection or ornamentation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
